import React from "react";
import { StyleSheet, Image, Text, View, ImageBackground } from "react-native";

            style={styles.Group}
            source={{
              uri: "https://firebasestorage.googleapis.com/v0/b/unify-bc2ad.appspot.com/o/9hdejqknpam-491%3A731?alt=media&token=c49cf7cf-800f-472d-af6e-2ab1a47b208a",
            }}

            }}

            }}
          />
        </View>
        <View style={styles.Group335}>
          <Text style={styles.Txt1066}>LOGO</Text>
          <Text style={styles.Txt772}>LOGIN</Text>
          <View style={styles.Group10579}>
            <Text style={styles.Txt298}>Phone Number</Text>
            <View style={styles.Content}>
              <Text style={styles.Txt173}>98170</Text>
            </View>
          </View>
          <View style={styles.TextInput}>
            <Text style={styles.Txt498}>Password</Text>
            <View style={styles.Content1}>
              <Text style={styles.Txt859}>Enter your pin</Text>
              <Image
                style={styles.IconlyLightOutlineHide}

                  uri: "https://firebasestorage.googleapis.com/v0/b/unify-bc2ad.appspot.com/o/9hdejqknpam-493%3A920?alt=media&token=9f53b714-e1b5-4a0a-bd07-73aec61ad09e",
                }}
              />
            </View>
          </View>
          <View style={styles.Group5101}>
            <View style={styles.Box} />
            <Text style={styles.Txt323}>Remember me</Text>
            <Text style={styles.Txt053}>Forgot Password?</Text>
          </View>
          <View style={styles.Button}>
            <Text style={styles.Txt1047}>LOGIN</Text>
          </View>
        </View>
        <Text style={styles.multiple1}>Don’t have an account? Register</Text>
      </View>
    </View>
  );
}
